<tr>
<td width="10"><img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/SmallNew.gif" border="0" alt="New Message"></td><td width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>How do we make money? (modified 0 times)</b> </font></td><td width="50%" align="RIGHT"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>Slith</b></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td><a href="UltraBoard.cgi?Action=ShowProfile&ID=slith&Board=magician&Idle=30&Sort=0&Order=Descend&Page=0&Session=" target="Profile" OnMouseOver="window.status='View Slith (slith) Profile.';return true;" OnMouseOut="window.status=''"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="000000 ">Profile</font></a></td><td align="RIGHT"></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="EEEEEE">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Small question I have with Magicians, it is all opinions and if you can help me with it, I would appreciate it. How do we make money? I mean, if you look at the other classes that cast, we really don't have a way of making cash. <p>

Druids - Port, Buff, Sow, Heal<br>
Shaman - Buff, Sow, Heal<br>
Wizard - Port<br>
Necros - Locate corpse, Soon to be a res, Heal<br>
Enchanter - Enchant all metals, making jewelry &lt;Won't mention Moggok quest, it can   be          done by anyone, just work that faction up&gt;, Clarity<br>
Rangers - Buffs, Small heals<br>
Clerics - Buffs, Res, Exp Res, Heal<br>
Mages - Nothing. Now if someone says summon stuff, someone going to get smashed. Oh oh! Selling stacks of summoned food and water, 1pp a stack, weapons &lt;Noone ever wants, MAYBE a mod rod, but then they usually don't pay&gt; heat/cold stones, waterstones arrows anything. Nothing really makes us cash. I struggle every day with cash problems and well, before all the other classes slam me, bards can do healings also and corpse retrieve. Also guiding since you get selos. Warriors have a problem probably also. I haven't mentioned SK or Monks cuase I have no idea what they can do as I really never have played one. But I didn't mention other classes, I mentioned casting classes.<p>

--Shadowstepper, Poor Magi of Karana<br>
        --Rodcet Nife</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER">
