<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Banking for other PC's is an excellent way to make money. This is what i did. When i got to lvl 12 i bought bind. I would bind myself at the bank in High Keep, invis myself and run to South Karana and bank people's change for them. People usually give you anywhere 5-20pp just for banking for them and all you got to do is gate back to the bank cash in your change and go back and do it again. After about 4 hours of this I had well over 350pp in just 1 day. Save up around 20pp to start and just watch your bank account grow. 20+ levels later im still at it. At first it's slow but once you get a decent pile of Platinum it becomes much easier. I got around 5k in the bank right now and thats after i bought all my spells and equipment up to this level and i guaruntee you most of that is profit from banking <img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/Happy.gif" border="0" align="middle"></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
