<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Ok, I've made a few levels since my last post on this thread, this is what I've learned:<p>

Lvl 19 - 22<br>
As noted elsewhere on this board the hermit in s. karana is good exp and fair loot. He's soloable, drops up 2.5 - 3 pp and sometimes fine steel. He's in the far s.e. corner of the zone. Watch out for the wandering gnoll.<p>

Lvl 20 - 24<br>
The two treants that spawn in the n.e. corner of s. karana.  Get in a group, there may be a waiting list, but it's worth it. On my server (V.Z.) it's customary for everyone to turn lootsplit OFF and then loot both treants when your turn comes up.  The treants drop 1 - 3 pp, AND up to around 30 g & lightstones. I wind up throwing the copper away because I'm carrying so damn much silver & gold.  You will blow your faction in Qeynos to h*ll but if you can live with that you can knock down some good cash.  Experience seems to come slowly as there are often lvl 28-29's sucking it up, but as you gain a few levels exp gets better.<p>

Lvl 24 - <br>
The single treant in w. karana (+1215, -8350). Spawns every 5 min, drops similar loot as the dual-spawn in s.k. You can solo this guy and keep all the cash for yourself. At 24 most of the spawns con yellow, some blue or white, rarely red. Be prepared to go in and take some licks for your pet.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
